VERSION: 6.3.2
MANUFACTURER: Espressif Systems & PlatformIO Labs (Open Source)
REQUIREMENTS: To provide hardware abstraction layers (HAL), peripheral drivers (GPIO, I2C, SPI), and Wi-Fi/Bluetooth stacks.
